flowchart TD
    subgraph "Memory Models"
        T[Tiny<br/>Code + Data < 64KB<br/>All near pointers]
        S[Small<br/>Code < 64KB<br/>Data < 64KB<br/>Near pointers]
        M[Medium<br/>Code > 64KB<br/>Data < 64KB<br/>Far code, near data]
        C[Compact<br/>Code < 64KB<br/>Data > 64KB<br/>Near code, far data]
        L[Large<br/>Code > 64KB<br/>Data > 64KB<br/>All far pointers]
        H[Huge<br/>Code > 64KB<br/>Data > 64KB<br/>Far pointers + segment math]
    end

    T --> |"More memory needed"| S
    S --> |"More code"| M
    S --> |"More data"| C
    M --> |"More data"| L
    C --> |"More code"| L
    L --> |"Arrays > 64KB"| H
